<HL>
   K-III Holdings Completes Deal
</HL>
<DATE>
06/06/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A18
</SO>
<CO>
   T.TOC
</CO>
<IN>
TENDER OFFERS, MERGERS, ACQUISITIONS (TNM)
</IN>
<LP>
   NEW YORK -- K-III Holdings Limited Partnership, an
affiliate of the investment bank Kohlberg Kravis Roberts &amp;
Co. here, said it completed the purchase of Ward's
Communications, which produces publications providing data to
the automotive industry, from Thomson Corp., a Toronto-based
publishing company. Terms weren't disclosed.
